{"about_the_game":"Taken Away is a non-linear strategic horror game. Following a car &quot;accident&quot;, you have been abducted. Explore your surroundings, don't get caught, figure out a way to escape... or face a gruesome death.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/vert1.png?t=1738927295\" /><br><br>Every game is unique, each run starts with a random setup: items placement changes, passwords are randomly generated. The Dog and the Man's behaviors can be unpredictable, and should be handled with care.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/vert2.png?t=1738927295\" /><br><br>You will face many hurdles and challenges, making it alive will be tough...<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Searching the house is the #1 key to your success, but the Man doesn't really like it...<br></li><li>His pet Wolf doesn't like you either, stay low.<br></li><li>Avoid traps, pick locks, listen carefully to all sound cues and be smarter than the enemy!<br></li><li>Play a video game inside the game!<br></li><li>Grab some vegetables, and make soup! Might be useful, who knows...<br></li><li>What is this strange growl coming from the basement?</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/tvgame.gif?t=1738927295\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/lockpick.gif?t=1738927295\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/accident.gif?t=1738927295\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"FREE HUGS","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1322090/2ccf1d4e2be5e6202962a64246f5cbfed60be5f7.jpg"},{"name":"HELLO THERE!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/